Successfully deployed, investigated, monitored, and removed an Nginx container while learning the most commonly used Docker commands used in real-world DevOps and Cloud Engineering environments.

This lab forms the foundation for all future Docker, Kubernetes, ECS, EKS, and containerized application deployments.
